The Media Lions celebrate the context of creativity. Entries need to demonstrate an inspiring and innovative implementation of ideas in work that's enhanced and amplified by a game-changing channel strategy. #CannesLions2017: Media shortlistThe Cannes Lions Media shortlist has been released, with a single SA campaign making the cut...23 hours ago Native VML&#x2019;s Absolut: One Source campaign, with production by Egg Films, media by Vizeum Cape Town, PR by Capacity Relations and additional work by Enterprise Republic, was awarded a Bronze Lion in the category: 'Use of Branded Content created for Digital or Social Media'. Special awards on the night included 'Media Person of the Year'. This went to Universal Music Group CEO and founder Sir Lucian Grainge, credited with "saving the music industry", while Media Network of the Year went to OMD. A post shared by Khaled Aouij (@khaledaouij) on Jun 21, 2017 at 10:50am PDT The Grand Prix went to R/GA New York for Jet.com&#x2019;s &#x2018;Innovating Saving&#x2019;. View the full table of winning work below: Media Lions Winners EntrantTitleClientProductAwardR/GA, New YorkINNOVATING SAVINGJET.COMJET.COMGrand Prix McCANN NEW YORKFEARLESS GIRLSTATE STREET GLOBAL ADVISORSSHE ETFGold LionCOLENSO BBDO, AucklandTHE CHILD REPLACEMENT PROGRAMMEMARS NZPEDIGREEGold LionJ. WALTER THOMPSON COLOMBIA, Bogot / GLUE COLUMBIA, Bogot EQUALITY SIGNS NIKE COLOMBIANIKE WOMENGold LionFCB MOSCOWULTIMATE GIVING PLEASUREBMW RUSSIABMW AUTOMOBILEGold LionMcCANN NEW YORKFEARLESS GIRLSTATE STREET GLOBAL ADVISORSSHE ETFGold LionSAATCHI & SAATCHI, New YorkBRADSHAW STAINP&GTIDEGold LionCLEMENGER BBDO MELBOURNEHUNGERITHMMARS CHOCOLATE AUSTRALIASNICKERS Gold LionSAATCHI & SAATCHI, New YorkBRADSHAW STAINP&GTIDEGold LionMANNING GOTTLIEB OMD, London / adam&eveDDB, LondonNO ONE SHOULD HAVE NO ONEAGE UKAGE UKGold LionCLEMENGER BBDO SYDNEYSOUPTUBECAMPBELL ARNOTTSCAMPBELLSSilver LionY&R MADRIDBROKEN HEARTSFIESTAPIRULETA LOLLIPOPSilver LionTBWA\RAAD, DubaiCAMELPOWERN